Organization

The board of Quina Care:

J.C. (Cootje) Bouwman-Zaaijer

{% image src="/images/raw/2017/06/mariska-circular-xs.jpg" align="center" /%}

M.A.E. (Mariska) van de Sande

{% image src="/images/raw/2017/06/yvonne-circular-xs.jpg" align="center" /%}

Y. (Yvonne) van der Ende

chairman

secretary

treasurer

chaiman@quinacare.org

secretary@quinacare.org

treasurer@quinacare.org

Cootje has worked in the Ministry of Defense. Here she occupied various consultancy and supervising positions and the last years as deputy director of the department of Organization and Formation. She recently retired. Cootje has no management/advisory duties at other organizations.

Mariska works as a radiation oncologist in the Verbeeten Institute, an institute of radiation and nuclear medicine. During her medicine studies she has worked for a few months in a rural part of Surinam. Mariska has no management/advisory duties at other organizations.

Yvonne is director of finance, HR, and IT at *VIBA* and *Mavom*, two sistercompanies that are both specialized in joining techniques. Before she was the financial controller of the Lion Heart Foundation in Sierra Leone. Yvonne has no management/advisory duties at other organizations.

