The board of Quina Care serves on a voluntary basis.

Ambassador of Quina Care:

{% image src="/images/raw/2019/07/floris.jpg" align="center" /%}

Floris van der Sman

ambassador

floris.vandersman@quinacare.org

Floris is a behavioural biologist and currently works at IVN. They intend to reconnect people with nature and try to rebalance the harmony between human and nature. His passion is with animals and nature. He works as a volunteer at a sustainable dairy farm and gives guest lectures on behalf of WWF. In his free time, he likes to go out into nature for a walk.

