chairman

secretary

treasurer

Medical doctor and working as a PhD-candidate in the Maxima Medical Center in Veldhoven. She is born and raised in Guayaquil, Ecuador.

Working as a specialist in International Health and Tropical Medicine in the Pastaza province of Ecuador.

Born in Guayaquil, the coastal region of Ecuador, and working as a general practitioner. At the moment she is studying a postgraduate in geriatrics in Buenos Aires.

