Donna Gianoulis

board member

board member

board member

Head of architectural design wokshop and teacher at the Faculty of Architecture and Urbanism of the Equator Technological University in Quito, Ecuador. Developing and designing furniture in *Atelier Design,* an own concept that he has created in the recent years. Fond of good cooking.

Founder of the tourist agency Southern Expeditions and marketing director at the brand My Adventure Ecuador. Both companies are based in Ecuador.

Donna Gianoulis, owner of Van Every Construction, California, USA now retired, has been a lifelong activist and supporter of people and causes committed to serving and strengthening the common good.  She delights in family & friends, music and theater, travel and the natural world.

